## Splunk Detection

### Key SPL Queries

**Failed login count over time:**
```spl
index=main EventCode=4625
| timechart count by src_ip
```

**Top attacking IPs:**
```spl
index=main EventCode=4625
| stats count by src_ip
| sort - count
```

**Brute force threshold alert:**
```spl
index=main EventCode=4625
| stats count by src_ip
| where count > 10
```

