## Lessons Learned

- Universal Forwarder silent install (`/quiet`) can cause credential lockout — use GUI installer instead
- Splunk initialized-but-no-users state requires full reinstall via `.deb` package
- EventID 4625 is the primary indicator for failed RDP brute force attempts

